{"tid":724851,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚睇完兩場波 突然覺得自己長大左","createTime":"2018-07-01T08:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T19:13:53.000Z","uid":81160,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bb25bc3024af1560703b1265b3c6da39c4768c0e","tid":724851,"uid":81160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:56:54.000Z","msg":"10年開始學睇波同踼波<br />\n見證住西甲盛世<br />\n英超唔再係BIG4壟斷  曼城 李城都做過冠軍<br />\n可能以後唔會再有兩位球王可以爭足十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n19歲既麥巴比已經做左國家英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而20歲既我仲係鳩流流咁唔知做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同齡入面己經有人有好大成就<br />\n個分野出緊嚟<br />\n當有一日人意識到依樣野<br />\n佢就開始長大<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01979cd380af21e3bf1cb23aeff8eaaeb45bf24","tid":724851,"uid":28281,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:04:22.000Z","msg":"樓豬得20歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389c5ce38256c7e3cdaea37dde75c5d08a55b389","tid":724851,"uid":81160,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"a01979cd380af21e3bf1cb23aeff8eaaeb45bf24","tid":724851,"uid":28281,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:04:22.000Z","msg":"樓豬得20歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:18:51.000Z","msg":"你都試過20歲既"},{"pid":"49289a16929755b6a7ff3b954fb8c3088f15822d","tid":724851,"uid":134924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:25:37.000Z","msg":"睇完阿葡兩場 我先數緊自己睇左幾多屆世盃 <br />\n94睇電視精華 98開始正式捱夜 02 06 10 14 18 <br />\n我直頭唔敢想像自己有意識計 已經經歷7屆世界盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"